{"tid":365804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本民前將出席明日聲援政治犯遊行","createTime":"2017-08-19T13:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T14:04:49.000Z","uid":92301,"like":114,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4d7baba844da6a269c2a4ee9d65681c9bd271e9","tid":365804,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:45:59.000Z","msg":"【聲援政治犯遊行】<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uh4tfbpi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuh4tfbpi&h=f0c239bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暴政底下，無人可以獨善其身。<br />\n<br />\n本土民主前線將出席明日聲援政治犯遊行，作最基本的政治表態。<br />\n<br />\n同時，本土民主前線希望藉參與是次遊行，提醒公眾於社會一隅尚有更多未受鎂光燈聚焦的政治打壓受害者，包括初一暴動案之被告人士。<br />\n<br />\n這群抗爭者或許抱持更加激進的政治主張，但同樣心懷改革社會的理想，爭取大眾之權益，應同樣受到尊重及關注。<br />\n<br />\n（是次遊行並非由本土民主前線發起，故並無特別行動。但若警方挑起衝突，本土民主前線將按照一貫原則保護示威者。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1952188838368352&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=1546925482228025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1952188838368352%26substory_index%3D0%26id%3D1546925482228025&d=VoAUQLZYd%2Fi1HvvGMv7jAF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=19b566ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1952188838368352&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=1546925482228025</a>"},{"pid":"91b9efe3ea077c91e2eb14a43635b8bf1649a18e","tid":365804,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:46:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38753873f200fb9bc4da3baaccef4b30b307f98b","tid":365804,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c646834643d7bd6c64eee75d335509bd568a164","tid":365804,"uid":79563,"like":24,"dislike":2,"sco